{"tid":2501940,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–害蟲反制植物的防禦機制","createTime":"2021-04-23T20:15:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T13:01:26.000Z","uid":38861,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b48b31ea245fdee59316d40a7131a4977b17a627","tid":2501940,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T20:15:16.000Z","msg":"植物雖無法躲避昆蟲的侵襲，但也並非是任蟲魚肉的存在。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTsj5tzugjAsFHEvusF3ssV3cmf6UroAP4ZSrYaf6HEZC?filename=noGahsO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnoGahsO.jpg&h=15791d48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n它們對抗外敵的其中一道方式，就是在葉子中製造一些對昆蟲有毒的化學物。<br />\n如果對方膽敢吃掉自己的話，下場就只有死路一條。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(圖2)圖中紅色結構的是葉子其中一種專用作對付昆蟲的有毒化學物(對人類及大部份動物無害)，而植物自身攜帶著一隻名為BtPMaT1的蛋白酶，它能夠將有毒的化學物改造成為無害化學物，相信是為了避免對付害蟲的時候會不慎毒害自己而設。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYaG9V4NX4EC9kn8rr77x2RkBxNWyat9TUcouKdQiSWhS?filename=Yswp6ma.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYswp6ma.png&h=dc309670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n換句話說，植物有著製作毒藥能力的同時，亦可製作相應的解藥自保。<br />\n<br />\n(圖3)然而，害蟲可不是吃素的(雖然的確是在吃素)，有科學家發現有部份害蟲身上竟然發展出跟植物一模一樣的BtPMaT1基因，相信是透過進食葉子時從中將該基因鑴在自己的基因圖譜裡頭，從而發展出對抗有毒化學物的方法。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSRnZFhKJJnVp1KmdfmKouUsfTGWnSgARAMpbLpykiEZX?filename=zb1ahsS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzb1ahsS.png&h=b0b5c62f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現在有不少科學家正在研究箇中的機制，若然能成功拆解箇中的秘密，分分中可以反其道而行，將只對害蟲有毒的基因注入在植物裡頭，讓害蟲們偷取後自取滅亡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzgxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=59574460\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzgxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=1d530519\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n <br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.cell.com/cell/fulltext/S0092-8674\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cell.com%2Fcell%2Ffulltext%2FS0092-8674&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzgxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=a4dfe52e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cell.com/cell/fulltext/S0092-8674</a>(21)00164-1"},{"pid":"68db90a1cb710363d2855ba5129b0986da0598a8","tid":2501940,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T20:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRPqzmtUX9b2kiFAUY4Lymd5cWTQsKbcM32qMFH74AJ8v?filename=Nw9dfer.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNw9dfer.gif&h=3c3c2223&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZpzECuHkVnMowYFnRkzY3q1u9AeCsARwaLsGLwXq5Q28?filename=fg5Px07.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffg5Px07.gif&h=8b60eee3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"321664d754c9d32d81ecca8d15b236bb8b6a02aa","tid":2501940,"uid":50745,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T20:45:46.000Z","m